Package amesmarket.filereaders

Classes for reading files.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IZoneIndexProvider
    Define a way to map zone names to array indices.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractConfigFileReader<T>
    Abstract reader for any file reader which is line based and uses "//" as a comment character.
    CaseFileReader
    Parse a case file.
    DictionaryReader
    A lexer/parser that reads python style dictionaries.
    IZoneIndexProvider.AutomaticIndexProvider
    A IZoneIndexProvider that automatically creates a new index for any name it does not know about.
    IZoneIndexProvider.DefaultIndexProvider
    An index provider that can go from a string of form prefix[1-9][0-9]* and strip off the prefix to get the zone index.
    IZoneIndexProvider.NamedIndexProvider
    A zone index provider that allows clients to set which name maps to which index.
    LoadCaseControlReader
    Read a load scenario control file and create a object representing that data.
    LoadCaseLabelInfo
    Models all the different pieces of information that may show up in a label in on of the master/aux/scenario load case files.
    LoadCaseScenarioReader
    Read in a data file representing a single LoadProfile scenario.
    LoadCaseVerifier  
    LoadProfileReader
    Read in a data file represting the load profile for each our of each day.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadDataFileFormatException
    An exception to represent a problem in the data file.
